{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 14,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 469.679,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.811,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 1.991,
      "end": 5.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if the Gentiles shall hearken unto the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.561,
      "end": 8.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in that day that he shall manifest himself unto them",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.085,
      "end": 10.153,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in word,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.333,
      "end": 11.866,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also in power,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 12.046,
      "end": 13.346,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in very deed,",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 13.526,
      "end": 16.452,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the taking away of their stumbling blocks\u2014",
      "verse": "14:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 17.132,
      "end": 20.615,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And harden not their hearts against the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 20.795,
      "end": 24.185,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be numbered among the seed of thy father;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 24.365,
      "end": 27.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, they shall be numbered among the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 27.564,
      "end": 31.047,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be a blessed people upon the promised land forever;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 31.227,
      "end": 34.431,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be no more brought down into captivity;",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 34.611,
      "end": 37.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the house of Israel shall no more be confounded.",
      "verse": "14:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 38.17,
      "end": 41.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And that great pit, which hath been digged for them",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 41.879,
      "end": 44.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 44.799,
      "end": 48.096,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was founded by the devil and his children,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 48.276,
      "end": 51.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might lead away the souls of men down to hell\u2014",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 51.8,
      "end": 54.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, that great pit which hath been digged",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 54.395,
      "end": 56.299,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the destruction of men",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 56.479,
      "end": 58.894,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be filled by those who digged it,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 59.074,
      "end": 61.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto their utter destruction,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 61.251,
      "end": 62.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb of God;",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 63.056,
      "end": 65.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "not the destruction of the soul,",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 65.326,
      "end": 68.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be the casting of it into that hell which hath no end.",
      "verse": "14:3",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 69.535,
      "end": 73.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, this is according to the captivity of the devil,",
      "verse": "14:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 73.43,
      "end": 76.077,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also according to the justice of God,",
      "verse": "14:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 76.257,
      "end": 80.947,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon all those who will work wickedness and abomination before him.",
      "verse": "14:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 81.627,
      "end": 85.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the angel spake unto me, Nephi, saying:",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 85.383,
      "end": 88.402,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou hast beheld that if the Gentiles repent",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 88.582,
      "end": 90.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it shall be well with them;",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 90.62,
      "end": 94.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou also knowest concerning the covenants of the Lord",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 94.515,
      "end": 96.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 96.413,
      "end": 100.639,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou also hast heard that whoso repenteth not must perish.",
      "verse": "14:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 101.319,
      "end": 103.966,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, wo be unto the Gentiles",
      "verse": "14:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 104.146,
      "end": 107.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they harden their hearts against the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "14:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 108.402,
      "end": 111.235,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the time cometh, saith the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 111.415,
      "end": 115.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I will work a great and a marvelous work among the children of men;",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 115.96,
      "end": 118.236,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a work which shall be everlasting,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 118.416,
      "end": 120.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "either on the one hand or on the other\u2014",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 121.15,
      "end": 124.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "either to the convincing of them unto peace and life eternal,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 125.138,
      "end": 128.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or unto the deliverance of them to the hardness of their hearts",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 128.847,
      "end": 130.983,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the blindness of their minds",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 131.163,
      "end": 134.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto their being brought down into captivity,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 134.547,
      "end": 136.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also into destruction,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 136.445,
      "end": 138.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both temporally and spiritually,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 138.993,
      "end": 141.64,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the captivity of the devil,",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 141.82,
      "end": 143.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I have spoken.",
      "verse": "14:7",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 144.172,
      "end": 148.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when the angel had spoken these words, he said unto me:",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 149.089,
      "end": 154.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Rememberest thou the covenants of the Father unto the house of Israel?",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 154.192,
      "end": 155.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I said unto him,",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 155.765,
      "end": 156.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea.",
      "verse": "14:8",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 157.142,
      "end": 159.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he said unto me:",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 159.876,
      "end": 160.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look,",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 161.031,
      "end": 163.91,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 164.09,
      "end": 166.784,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the mother of abominations,",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 166.964,
      "end": 168.729,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose founder is the devil.",
      "verse": "14:9",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 169.409,
      "end": 170.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said unto me:",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 171.122,
      "end": 173.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold there are save two churches only;",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 173.949,
      "end": 176.643,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the one is the church of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 176.823,
      "end": 179.099,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the other is the church of the devil;",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 179.279,
      "end": 183.737,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, whoso belongeth not to the church of the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 183.917,
      "end": 186.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "belongeth to that great church,",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 186.187,
      "end": 188.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the mother of abominations;",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 188.782,
      "end": 191.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she is the whore of all the earth.",
      "verse": "14:10",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 192.016,
      "end": 194.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I looked",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 194.472,
      "end": 197.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and beheld the whore of all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 197.206,
      "end": 199.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she sat upon many waters;",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 199.754,
      "end": 202.726,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she had dominion over all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 202.906,
      "end": 206.435,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all nations, kindreds, tongues, and people.",
      "verse": "14:11",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 207.115,
      "end": 211.434,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld the church of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 211.614,
      "end": 213.843,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and its numbers were few,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 214.023,
      "end": 219.549,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the wickedness and abominations of the whore who sat upon many waters;",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 219.729,
      "end": 222.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, I beheld that the church of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 223.113,
      "end": 225.156,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were the saints of God,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 225.336,
      "end": 227.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "were also upon all the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 228.117,
      "end": 231.6,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their dominions upon the face of the earth were small,",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 231.78,
      "end": 234.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the wickedness of the great whore whom I saw.",
      "verse": "14:12",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 235.618,
      "end": 240.726,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld that the great mother of abominations",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 240.906,
      "end": 244.993,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did gather together multitudes upon the face of all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 245.173,
      "end": 247.402,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all the nations of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 247.582,
      "end": 250.136,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to fight against the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "14:13",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 250.816,
      "end": 255.739,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, beheld the power of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 255.919,
      "end": 259.727,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it descended upon the saints of the church of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 259.907,
      "end": 262.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and upon the covenant people of the Lord,",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 262.734,
      "end": 266.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were scattered upon all the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 266.536,
      "end": 268.579,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were armed with righteousness",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 268.759,
      "end": 271.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with the power of God in great glory.",
      "verse": "14:14",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 271.807,
      "end": 274.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld that the wrath of God",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 275.006,
      "end": 278.768,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was poured out upon that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 278.948,
      "end": 282.57,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that there were wars and rumors of wars",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 282.75,
      "end": 285.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all the nations and kindreds of the earth.",
      "verse": "14:15",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 286.449,
      "end": 290.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as there began to be wars and rumors of wars",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 290.251,
      "end": 294.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among all the nations which belonged to the mother of abominations,",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 294.286,
      "end": 296.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 296.602,
      "end": 300.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, the wrath of God is upon the mother of harlots;",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 300.265,
      "end": 302.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold, thou seest all these things\u2014",
      "verse": "14:16",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 303.221,
      "end": 306.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when the day cometh that the wrath of God",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 306.234,
      "end": 308.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is poured out upon the mother of harlots,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 308.968,
      "end": 313.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the great and abominable church of all the earth,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 313.374,
      "end": 315.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose founder is the devil,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 315.551,
      "end": 317.269,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then, at that day,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 317.449,
      "end": 319.725,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the work of the Father shall commence,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 319.905,
      "end": 323.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in preparing the way for the fulfilling of his covenants,",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 323.8,
      "end": 328.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he hath made to his people who are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "14:17",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 328.845,
      "end": 331.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "14:18",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 332.136,
      "end": 332.972,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "14:18",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 333.652,
      "end": 335.556,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and beheld a man,",
      "verse": "14:19",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 335.736,
      "end": 337.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he was dressed in a white robe.",
      "verse": "14:19",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 338.645,
      "end": 340.456,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "14:20",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 340.636,
      "end": 343.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold one of the twelve apostles of the Lamb.",
      "verse": "14:20",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 344.195,
      "end": 346.331,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, he shall see and write",
      "verse": "14:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 346.511,
      "end": 348.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the remainder of these things;",
      "verse": "14:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 348.641,
      "end": 351.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and also many things which have been.",
      "verse": "14:21",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 351.829,
      "end": 354.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he shall also write concerning the end of the world.",
      "verse": "14:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 355.62,
      "end": 359.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the things which he shall write are just and true;",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 359.747,
      "end": 362.023,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold they are written in the book",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 362.203,
      "end": 365.407,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which thou beheld proceeding out of the mouth of the Jew;",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 365.587,
      "end": 369.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and at the time they proceeded out of the mouth of the Jew,",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 369.529,
      "end": 373.151,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, at the time the book proceeded out of the mouth of the Jew,",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 373.331,
      "end": 376.768,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which were written were plain and pure,",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 376.948,
      "end": 380.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and most precious and easy to the understanding of all men.",
      "verse": "14:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 380.925,
      "end": 382.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold,",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 382.359,
      "end": 385.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which this apostle of the Lamb shall write",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 385.79,
      "end": 388.205,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are many things which thou hast seen;",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 388.385,
      "end": 391.079,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold, the remainder shalt thou see.",
      "verse": "14:24",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 391.759,
      "end": 396.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But the things which thou shalt see hereafter thou shalt not write;",
      "verse": "14:25",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 396.49,
      "end": 399.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord God hath ordained the apostle of the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "14:25",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 399.967,
      "end": 401.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should write them.",
      "verse": "14:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 402.226,
      "end": 404.455,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also others who have been,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 404.635,
      "end": 406.864,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to them hath he shown all things,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 407.044,
      "end": 408.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they have written them;",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 408.989,
      "end": 410.8,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are sealed up",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 410.98,
      "end": 413.07,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to come forth in their purity,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 413.25,
      "end": 415.758,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth which is in the Lamb,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 415.938,
      "end": 418.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the own due time of the Lord,",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 418.626,
      "end": 420.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "14:26",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 420.931,
      "end": 423.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, heard and bear record,",
      "verse": "14:27",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 423.805,
      "end": 426.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the name of the apostle of the Lamb was John,",
      "verse": "14:27",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 427.143,
      "end": 429.511,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the word of the angel.",
      "verse": "14:27",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 430.191,
      "end": 433.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, I, Nephi, am forbidden that I should write",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 433.761,
      "end": 437.198,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the remainder of the things which I saw and heard;",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 437.378,
      "end": 440.907,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore the things which I have written sufficeth me;",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 441.087,
      "end": 445.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I have written but a small part of the things which I saw.",
      "verse": "14:28",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 445.854,
      "end": 447.479,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I bear record",
      "verse": "14:29",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 447.659,
      "end": 450.678,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I saw the things which my father saw,",
      "verse": "14:29",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 450.858,
      "end": 453.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the angel of the Lord did make them known unto me.",
      "verse": "14:29",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 454.603,
      "end": 458.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I make an end of speaking concerning the things which I saw",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 458.916,
      "end": 461.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "while I was carried away in the Spirit;",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 461.372,
      "end": 464.066,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if all the things which I saw are not written,",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 464.246,
      "end": 466.475,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which I have written are true.",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 466.655,
      "end": 468.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus it is.",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 468.182,
      "end": 469.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "14:30",
      "lineIndex": 155
    }
  ]
}